						<h4><span class="label label-premium"><i class="icon-ok icon-white"> </i></span> Premium Mission</h4>
						<p>Depending on your experience with the platform, you can take part in less or more missions. Therefore you should choose them carefully. The number of contributions at any one time is set at 3 by default. You will receive an email, should this limit change.<br>As premium missions automatically end up in writing jobs, contributors will be selected within the 2 hours following the quote request deadline. If you are not selected, the mission is removed from your number of contributions. If you are selected, the mission is only removed from your number of contributions once the article sent has been approved by Edit-place.</p>
						<hr>
						<h4><span class="label label-quote"><i class="icon-ok icon-white"> </i></span> Freedom Mission</h4>
						<p>The number of contributions is accounted for in the same way for Freedom missions. If your contribution limit is set to 3, you can therefore not take part in more than 3 missions regardless of their type.<br>As a Freedom mission can only be a quote request, and not necessarily result in a writing job, we ask you to add an expiry date to your offer. Once the deadline has been reached, if the client hasn't selected any writers, your offer will be removed from your number of contributions.</p>
						<hr>
						<h4><span class="label label-quote-premium"><i class="icon-ok icon-white"> </i></span> Premium Quote</h4>
						<p> As this is only a quote request, the contribution limit does not apply to premium quotes. If the quote becomes a Premium mission, the best quotes will be given an exclusive deadline to take part in the Premium mission and to offer a rate again.</p>
