						<h4><span class="label label-premium"><i class="icon-ok icon-white"> </i></span> DEADLINE TO SET YOUR RATES</h4>

						<p>
							This is the timeframe you have to take part and set your rates. Once the time has elapsed, you will no longer be able to take part in the mission. This is set by the client for Freedom missions and by Edit-place for Premium missions/quotes.
							
						</p>	 
						<h4><span class="label label-quote"><i class="icon-ok icon-white"> </i></span> DEADLINE TO SEND YOUR ARTICLE</h4>
						<p>
							From the moment you are selected, the countdown starts and you will receive an email stating how long you have left to send your article. You will also find this deadline in your ongoing contributions. If for some unforeseen reason you are unable to send your article in time, you can ask for an extension, but only if the original deadline hasn't expired. This request must remain a one-off and isn't necessarily agreed. If this is the case, the mission will be taken away from you.
						</p>	
						<h4><span class="label label-quote-premium"><i class="icon-ok icon-white"> </i></span> DEADLINE TO REWRITE/AMEND YOUR ARTICLE</h4>
						<p>
							If a rewrite/amendment is requested by the client (Freedom mission) or Edit-place (Premium mission), you will receive an email stating how long you have to change your article. You will also find this deadline in your ongoing contributions.
						 </p>

