					<div class="tab-pane" id="pricing">
						<h4><span class="label label-premium"><i class="icon-ok icon-white"> </i></span> Premium Mission</h4>
						<p>
						  A price range is offered for each premium mission.<br>
						  You then have to offer your own rate within this price range, bearing in mind that this is a key factor when selecting profiles. <br>
						  If you are selected, the rate that you have offered is the rate that you will be paid once the mission has been confirmed.<br>
						</p>
						<hr>
						<h4><span class="label label-quote"><i class="icon-ok icon-white"> </i></span> Freedom Mission</h4>
						<p>						  
						  During freedom missions, no price range is set. Therefore you have to offer your rate. </p>
						  
						<hr>
						<h4><span class="label label-quote-premium"><i class="icon-ok icon-white"> </i></span> Premium Quote</h4>
						<p>
							A premium quote may or may not come with a price range. You will find all the information on the page after you click on the "My selection" button. 
						</p>
						
						<p><strong>Note</strong>&nbsp;: Edit-Place reserves the right to change the rate offered if the article could not be written or cannot be written (already existing....)</p>

